{
  "page": "Dragonstone (hill)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Essos.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Essos and the location of Dragonstone\"><img alt=\"Essos and the location of Dragonstone\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/350px-Essos.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/525px-Essos.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/700px-Essos.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 55.6%; left: 76.4%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px;\"><img alt=\"Essos and the location of Dragonstone\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Dragonstone\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 90%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Dragonstone</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> and the location of Dragonstone\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Dragonstone</b> is the name <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> gives to a hill in the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_sea\" title=\"Dothraki sea\">Dothraki sea</a>, naming it after her birthplace, the island of <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone_(island)\" title=\"Dragonstone (island)\">Dragonstone</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is located east of <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Diaf\" title=\"Vaes Diaf\">Vaes Diaf</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafjourneys.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafjourneys.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Geography\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Geography</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Geography\">Geography</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dragonstone_(hill)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Geography\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Daenerys_at_Dragonstone_Hill_by_Wyatt_Abernathy.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/Daenerys_at_Dragonstone_Hill_by_Wyatt_Abernathy.jpg/350px-Daenerys_at_Dragonstone_Hill_by_Wyatt_Abernathy.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"469\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/Daenerys_at_Dragonstone_Hill_by_Wyatt_Abernathy.jpg/525px-Daenerys_at_Dragonstone_Hill_by_Wyatt_Abernathy.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8c/Daenerys_at_Dragonstone_Hill_by_Wyatt_Abernathy.jpg/700px-Daenerys_at_Dragonstone_Hill_by_Wyatt_Abernathy.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Daenerys_at_Dragonstone_Hill_by_Wyatt_Abernathy.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Drogon\" title=\"Drogon\">Drogon</a> at Dragonstone, by Wyatt Abernathy ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The hill appears as a stony island within the green grassland of the Dothraki plains. Scrub grass and thorny bushes cover its lower slopes, while a jagged tangle of bare rock thrusts into the sky. There is a shallow cave amidst the broken boulders, razor-sharp ridges, and needle spires. There are fish in a nearby spring-fed pool.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dragonstone_(hill)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dragonstone_(hill)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After having fled <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a> atop the <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Drogon\" title=\"Drogon\">Drogon</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> ends up in the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_sea\" title=\"Dothraki sea\">Dothraki sea</a>. She stays in the dragon's lair, a cave in a hill that she names Dragonstone. She lives on local edible vegetation, and on meat from kills that Drogon brings back, and catches one fish from the pool.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Daenerys eventually decides to return to Meereen, but is unable to get Drogon to follow her commands, leading to her traveling on foot. She follows a stream that she thinks will flow into the <a href=\"/index.php/Skahazadhan\" title=\"Skahazadhan\">Skahazadhan</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dragonstone_(hill)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_71\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 71\">Chapter 71</a>, Daenerys X.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafjourneys.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafjourneys.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Journeys.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404200205\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.026 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.027 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 719/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12474/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4455/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1500/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 11/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1809/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   17.246      1 -total\n 44.89%    7.742      5 Template:Ref\n 42.51%    7.332      1 Template:Location_map\n 38.71%    6.676      1 Template:Location_map+\n 25.76%    4.442      5 Template:Ref/core\n 25.37%    4.375      1 Template:Location_map~\n 10.48%    1.807      1 Template:References\n  9.38%    1.618     10 Template:Location_map_Essos\n  5.02%    0.866      2 Template:Location_map/decdeg\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:17993-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404200205 and revision id 325777\n -->\n",
